tei:ab.tei:seg:
From Oppel (letter): a report on his lecture in
                 Halle;
              the performance of a work by him was called off.

In the afternoon, study of the revised copy of the "Eroica";
              dictation: performance of the second movement in two footnotes for Der freie
                    Satz.

Rf.: Frau Stransky singt italienische Arien;
              Zigeuner spielen unter anderem den Rakocy-Marsch
              in Berlioz’ Fassung.
